Baravar Cloakshadow is a lesser deity of the Gnomish Pantheon. His portfolio includes deception, hatred of goblin-kin, illusion, protection, traps, and wards. He is neutral good in Alignment. His Realm, the Hidden Knoll, lies in the Golden Hills in Bytopia. 

